{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/Spin10/Basic.html#Spin10Model.inclSM_eq_inclSMThruGeorgiGlashow\"><span class=\"name\">Spin10Model</span>.<span class=\"name\">inclSM_eq_inclSMThruGeorgiGlashow</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#InformalLemma\">InformalLemma</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The inclusion `inclSM` is equal to the inclusion `inclSMThruGeorgiGlashow`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/Spin10/Basic.html#Spin10Model.inclSM_eq_inclSMThruGeorgiGlashow","kind":"def","line":58,"name":"Spin10Model.inclSM_eq_inclSMThruGeorgiGlashow","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L58-L61"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/Spin10/Basic.html#Spin10Model.inclSMThruGeorgiGlashow\"><span class=\"name\">Spin10Model</span>.<span class=\"name\">inclSMThruGeorgiGlashow</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#InformalDefinition\">InformalDefinition</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The inclusion of the Standard Model gauge group into Spin(10), i.e., the composition of\n`inclGeorgiGlashow` and `GeorgiGlashow.inclSM`.\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/Spin10/Basic.html#Spin10Model.inclSMThruGeorgiGlashow","kind":"def","line":51,"name":"Spin10Model.inclSMThruGeorgiGlashow","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L51-L56"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/Spin10/Basic.html#Spin10Model.inclGeorgiGlashow\"><span class=\"name\">Spin10Model</span>.<span class=\"name\">inclGeorgiGlashow</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#InformalDefinition\">InformalDefinition</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The inclusion of the Georgi-Glashow gauge group into Spin(10), i.e., the Lie group homomorphism\nfrom `SU(n) → Spin(2n)` discussed on page 46 of https://math.ucr.edu/home/baez/guts.pdf for `n = 5`.\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/Spin10/Basic.html#Spin10Model.inclGeorgiGlashow","kind":"def","line":44,"name":"Spin10Model.inclGeorgiGlashow","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L44-L49"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/Spin10/Basic.html#Spin10Model.inclSM\"><span class=\"name\">Spin10Model</span>.<span class=\"name\">inclSM</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#InformalDefinition\">InformalDefinition</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The inclusion of the Standard Model gauge group into Spin(10), i.e., the composition of\n`embedPatiSalam` and `PatiSalam.inclSM`.\n\nSee page 56 of https://math.ucr.edu/home/baez/guts.pdf\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/Spin10/Basic.html#Spin10Model.inclSM","kind":"def","line":35,"name":"Spin10Model.inclSM","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L35-L42"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/Spin10/Basic.html#Spin10Model.inclPatiSalam\"><span class=\"name\">Spin10Model</span>.<span class=\"name\">inclPatiSalam</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#InformalDefinition\">InformalDefinition</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The inclusion of the Pati-Salam gauge group into Spin(10), i.e., the lift of the embedding\n`SO(6) × SO(4) → SO(10)` to universal covers, giving a homomorphism `Spin(6) × Spin(4) → Spin(10)`.\nPrecomposed with the isomorphism, `PatiSalam.gaugeGroupISpinEquiv`, between `SU(4) × SU(2) × SU(2)`\nand `Spin(6) × Spin(4)`.\n\nSee page 56 of https://math.ucr.edu/home/baez/guts.pdf\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/Spin10/Basic.html#Spin10Model.inclPatiSalam","kind":"def","line":24,"name":"Spin10Model.inclPatiSalam","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L24-L33"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/Spin10/Basic.html#Spin10Model.GaugeGroupI\"><span class=\"name\">Spin10Model</span>.<span class=\"name\">GaugeGroupI</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#InformalDefinition\">InformalDefinition</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The gauge group of the Spin(10) model, i.e., the group `Spin(10)`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/Spin10/Basic.html#Spin10Model.GaugeGroupI","kind":"def","line":19,"name":"Spin10Model.GaugeGroupI","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L19-L22"}}],"imports":["Init","PhysLean.Particles.BeyondTheStandardModel.PatiSalam.Basic","PhysLean.Particles.BeyondTheStandardModel.GeorgiGlashow.Basic"],"instances":[],"name":"PhysLean.Particles.BeyondTheStandardModel.Spin10.Basic"}